titlealts.searchtitle: Data Element: INVASIVE BREAST CANCER DETECTION RATE INVASIVE SIZE LESS THAN 10mm (PER 1,000 SCREENED) - Description

body.p: INVASIVE BREAST CANCER DETECTION RATE INVASIVE SIZE LESS THAN 10mm (PER 1,000 SCREENED) is the rate of invasive breast cancers smaller than 10mm detected, per 1,000 screened.
